{"tid":457150,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】衝動購物真係好爽 Day142 3/11","createTime":"2017-11-03T14:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T17:13:26.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"56edf0abe8d5ef0ce5776b7ffd81f28534f50af6","tid":457150,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=DInV5Kwn2B2D1XXUe0Kj026kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2d84deb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，開台前或者有任何突發事唔開都會Po上FB。<br />\n有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=DInV5Kwn2B2D1XXUe0Kj026kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=961fb447\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NRSeWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNRSeWz.jpg&h=f4a261d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我亦開左個Youtuber Page放開台嘅Backup<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg&d=DInV5Kwn2B2D1XXUe0Kj026kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2b98110b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">請各位多多支持，比D錢黎洗下</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"660b5628db57f8d60dbd44bca7713921ae470a5a","tid":457150,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:01:00.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95d2c8ff8579f2bf4a801d5391056c2ef2f4c3b","tid":457150,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b363e2bbe7d3b47188e4a45a26ed7152af0badbf","tid":457150,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe063862a6bafcac34d72bfaa1805cd769e96e87","tid":457150,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d186da20b80b49a6a407fb7a4d662e2bb47b7f2","tid":457150,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b543284ac51794b4331e40474498653fa911f61","tid":457150,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24e65616d4039b3e7a6c38e71ac20a342e5a57a","tid":457150,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4abdeaa445892fad7e4b4db5209f4e8ca0a062","tid":457150,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:28:55.000Z","ms